        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> In the depths of a cave under the Shattered Hills, is the lair of the hydra!<BR>From here it ravages the lands around, wreaking havoc for miles.<BR>Blumpkin, a warrior from the far North, a barbarian once, now a mercenary captain between wars, thought this would be an ideal foe, to test his mettle, and garner fame, he is not subtle, he enjoys the heft of a blade and the chance to fight a worthy foe.<BR>The gnomish mine nearby had been attacked several times by the brute, and there he enlisted the aid of Knok, a wizard small by comparison to the barbarian, but his powers are not to be taken lightly.<BR>The gnome mine was also where they met Cloauk, an elven rogue, jailed for a rowdy bar fight. The chnace of a quick parole and the gold literring the watery lair of the monster was soooooo tempting<BR>So the three tracked down, and assaulted the Hydra...<BR>Who will win?<BR>Cloauk has paralyzed one of the horror's necks with arrows dipped in wyvern venom.<BR>Knok has entranced one head, while his rune wards and enchantnments of speed let Blumpkin cleave with fury, and so far, avoided being crunched in the jaws of death.<BR>People from Poser 3, clothes, armour and textures mostly by myself, rendered in bryce 5, after work in Paint Shop Pro :)</P><P>This is based partially on EQ, Knok the gnome wizard, Blumpkin the barbarian warrior and Cloauk the wood elf rogue arepals I play with :)<BR>Hope no one minds me posting?</P><P>Redorious<BR>Archmage<BR>Karana</P><P><img src="http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/hydra_normal.jpg" border=0></P><P><a href="http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excalibur2thumb.jpg" border=0></a></font></td>

